content: Hello is there anyone here from CVS technology / QR issuer team.

@sonia nair I moved your two posts into a new topic. When posting, either search for an existing topic that's related to your question, or change the topic text to a new one that reflects what you want to talk about.
When you say "CVS technology", are you referring to a particular company? Product?
You may want to try the #smart/health-cards stream
Yes , whoever / whichever team is responsible for QR issuance in CVS Health
They're not likely to be on this as this zulip is targetted to FHIR developers. You'd need to contact CVS Health directly
There likely is someone from that group on the #smart/health-cards stream, I just do not know enough to point further.
